Building Material Companies | About | Summit Materials
































Jump to navigation



Summit Materials













 
  





About.











Our Vision.Summit Materials was formed to acquire and grow heavy-side building materials companies in the aggregates, ready-mix concrete, cement, asphalt paving and construction industries.  By teaming up with established local businesses, we are committed to creating value, providing access to growth capital, implementing best practices, and offering a safe place to work while striving to exceed our environmental and social responsibilities.
 
Learn more about how we see grassroots.










Meet the Summit Team.
Get to know us. 











What Binds Us.




SafetyIt’s our culture and ingrained in everything we do. It’s protecting our best assets -- our people.




ResponsibilityDoing it right the first time. Standing behind our products and services to meet the needs of our customers.




OpportunityMaintaining a local presence to bring growth to, and connect with, our communities.










Our Story.Summit Materials was formed in 2008, when Tom Hill and a small team of investors with a bold vision formed a new kind of building materials company. The company was founded around a single, simple idea: to bring successful companies together into something even greater. Summit brings value to its family of companies by maintaining entrepreneurial spirit and local presence, while providing access to resources and shared best practices. Since Summit's formation, the company has completed more than 43 acquisitions forming 12 platform companies operating in 24 states and British Columbia, Canada. These companies provide aggregates, cement, ready-mix, asphalt, and construction services to meet residential, nonresidential, and public demand.






Meet Our Family.


 
  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  
 







