Summit Materials, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 6:15 PM ET
Construction Materials

Company Overview of Summit Materials, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Summit Materials, LLC, together with its subsidiaries, operates as a construction materials company in the United States and Canada. It company operates through the West, East, and Cement segments. The company produces and sells aggregates, cement, ready-mixed concrete, and asphalt paving mix, as well as concrete products and plastics components. It also provides paving and related services. As of December 31, 2016, the company operated 171 quarries and sand deposits; 2 cement plants; 10 cement distribution terminals; 84 fixed and portable ready-mix concrete plants; and 47 asphalt paving mix plants, as well as landfill sites. It serves public infrastructure, residential construction, and non...
Summit Materials, LLC, together with its subsidiaries, operates as a construction materials company in the United States and Canada. It company operates through the West, East, and Cement segments. The company produces and sells aggregates, cement, ready-mixed concrete, and asphalt paving mix, as well as concrete products and plastics components. It also provides paving and related services. As of December 31, 2016, the company operated 171 quarries and sand deposits; 2 cement plants; 10 cement distribution terminals; 84 fixed and portable ready-mix concrete plants; and 47 asphalt paving mix plants, as well as landfill sites. It serves public infrastructure, residential construction, and nonresidential construction markets. The company was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Denver, Colorado. Summit Materials, LLC is a subsidiary of Summit Materials, Inc.
Detailed Description


